{
  "stem": "18520.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they came out [INAUDIBLE] [? die ?] maker So I lift up a hand, and I stood on my feet.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I stood-- oh, oh, my god.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't-- I forgot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That doesn't work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's going to be in it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER] Sorry, I almost ripped it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, so I-- I-- I-- I stood up here, you know, automatic, without thinking, lifting up the hand.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[POINTING] But that's a little different.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is a photographer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you know, I'm smiling with my tears.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So anyway, so I lifted up, and I stood on my toes to see that I'm big man, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm not a little boy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they-- everybody-- you're out, out, out, out, out, out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I went to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The trucks.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Going, and going-- I don't know, 10 days, five days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know, you're--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sit packed in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When-- they put you in a-- in a block.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember either.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- was-- it was about 50 people in-- I think 40 or 50 people in the barrack.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the barrack was built in such a way that the roof goes down into the earth.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And grass grows on it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not the roof there, but it's not [INAUDIBLE] so that it's flat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a lot of-- this place is big.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and you walked in lower.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was wooden-- the whole length with wood.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it was maybe 50 people in the barrack.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "50 people.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they're laying like-- like this, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And just wood.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There used to be a little hay on the-- on this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, there was a kapo.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a blockalteste and a kapo.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
